 create peace of mind for family members, and increase efficiency for health care practitioners, patients must come first.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>He envisioned a healthcare system that keeps  patients connected…<br><br>To give them a voice.<br>To improve equitable access.<br>To give  family members peace of mind. <br>To have companionship throughout their health journey.<br>To distribute care amongst practitioners.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-34_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-35_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/7650/1296/t/20/assets/skiinearlyaccessprogram-1639505220635.jpg?v=1639505222" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/7650/1296/t/20/assets/skiinearlyaccessprogram-1639505220635.jpg?v=1639505222 1536w" width="2100" height="1100"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-edc4" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-jHkVzv kFoSDU pf-36_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-dVNjXY gaVfQc"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-37_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-38_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-39_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-41_"><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Challenges We Face Today...</span></span></h3><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-42_ pf-r pf-c-ct pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:17px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-43_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-44_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/7650/1296/t/20/assets/icon-figures--mission22-1656359961903.png?v=1656359963" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/7650/1296/t/20/assets/icon-figures--mission22-1656359961903